<doc id="1004739" wikidata="Q3556146" url="?curid=1004739" title="Savalia">
<text>Savalia (Greek: Σαβάλια) is a village in the municipal unit of Amaliada, Elis, southern Greece. It is in the plains near the Ionian Sea, northwest of Roviata, southwest of Ampelokampos, east of Palaiochori, southeast of Gastouni, and northwest of Amaliada. The Greek National Road 9 (Patras–Pyrgos) passes southwest of the village. The railway from Patras to Pyrgos passes northeast of the village.

